CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 17, reads: "1. Original paintings of Budweiser Beer ads made the Budweiser booth a center of attraction to homemakers. Not shown are representatives, Wilford Vaux and William Porter."
TitMainTitle: Budweiser booth with original paintings of advertisements, beside Calvert whiskey booth, in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
